channel.title: Need help to find a source/w client 317
channel.description: I have searched all over runelocus, moparscape and google but I cant find a source/w client that is 317 and has all this bosses: Armadyl boss, bandos boss, zamorak boss, chaos ele and kbd. And a good skilling and training area. Ive found someone but they I couldnt dl or I a file from it was corrupt some help?

item.title: Need help to find a source/w client 317
item.dc:creator: @Svitkona Svitkona
item.description:
@Svitkona wrote:

kokosal:

Doesnt everybody say that delta sucks?

uhh yeah kind of, but you can do wonderful things with delta. most of the servers made in here are delta-based, and so are most of the tutorials. also, if you want something like that you’ll have to add it yourself, you can’t expect people to add all that just for you. i suggest you follow tutorials around here and learn to program then add everything yourself. trust me, you’ll be better off than if somebody just created it for you.
